OL,4,C'increasingly disturbing' online
OL,5,Cpornography
OL,7,FThe review led by Tory peer Baroness
OL,8,FGabby Bertin, warned that while
OL,9,Foffline pornographic content is
OL,10,Fregulated by the British Board of Film
OL,11,FClassification, there remains no
OL,12,F"safety net" for online pornography.
OL,14,FAs a result, violent pornographic
OL,15,Fcontent - for example material
OL,16,Fdepicting coercion - that would
OL,17,Ftypically be regarded as unfit for
OL,18,Foffline classification by the BBFC is
OL,19,Feasily accessible and "heavily
OL,20,Fpromoted" online.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
