OL,7,FIn a series of 32 recommendations
OL,8,Faimed at addressing this disparity,
OL,9,FBaroness Bertin argued that urgent
OL,10,Faction was needed to bring regulation
OL,11,Fup to speed with "increasingly
OL,12,Fdisturbing content" found online.
OL,14,FThe review published on Thursday has
OL,15,Fcalled for "violent, harmful and
OL,16,Fmisogynistic" pornographic content
OL,17,Falready illegal offline, such as that
OL,18,Fpromoting child sex abuse, to be made
OL,19,Fillegal online.
