OL,7,FWhile content depicting choking,
OL,8,Fincest and non-consensual intimate
OL,9,Fimages should also be made illegal.
OL,11,FBaroness Bertin said urgent action is
OL,12,Fneeded
OL,14,FBaroness Bertin warned that the
OL,15,Fpolicing of online pornographic
OL,16,Fcontent has been "low-priority and
OL,17,Freactive" and recommended the creation
OL,18,Fof a police database to develop a more
OL,19,Fconsistent approach across forces.
