OL,7,FAnd in light of what she described as
OL,8,F"total absence of government scrutiny
OL,9,Fof the sector", the Baroness also
OL,10,Frecommended giving one Whitehall
OL,11,Fdepartment clear oversight on
OL,12,Fpornography policy.
OL,14,FShe warned the proliferation of
OL,15,Funregulated violent pornography was
OL,16,Fhaving a particularly harmful impact
OL,17,Fon under 18s and was "rewiring" the
OL,18,Fway young people thought about gender
OL,19,Fand sex.
