OL,7,F"Misogynistic attitudes are on the
OL,8,Frise, with online spaces, including
OL,9,Fsome pornography sites, playing a
OL,10,Fsignificant role," she wrote in her
OL,11,Fforeword to the report.
OL,13,F"Worse, I have heard concerns from a
OL,14,Fwide range of experts of a potential
OL,15,Fassociation between people watching
OL,16,Fextreme (illegal) pornography and
OL,17,Fcommitting violent and sexual
OL,18,Foffences."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
