OL,7,FDavid Austin, Chief Executive of the
OL,8,FBritish Board of Film Classification,
OL,9,Fsaid there is a "growing body of
OL,10,Fevidence" that this is having a
OL,11,Fharmful impact on women and girls
OL,13,FDavid Austin, Chief Executive of the
OL,14,FBritish Board of Film Classification,
OL,15,Fsaid: "We did some research in 2020
OL,16,Fwhich found young women really
OL,17,Fconcerned about aggressive, violent
OL,18,Fpornography and young men acting out
OL,19,Fwhat they see in these kind of videos
OL,20,Fand many of them reported that they
OL,21,Fhad experienced that first-hand.
