OL,7,FOnline users will be able to use a
OL,8,Frange of methods such as credit card
OL,9,Fchecks and photo ID matching to
OL,10,Fconfirm their age.
OL,12,FPeter Kyle MP, Secretary of State for
OL,13,FScience, Innovation and Technology,
OL,14,Fsaid the government's new Online
OL,15,FSafety Act helps regulate online
OL,16,Fpornography but he will "do what it
OL,17,Ftakes" to make sure that children are
OL,18,Fprotected
