OL,7,FPeter Kyle MP, Secretary of State for
OL,8,FScience, Innovation and Technology,
OL,9,Fsaid: "The Online Safety Act is
OL,10,Fstrident in its powers. It also has
OL,11,Fpowers to compel companies that aren't
OL,12,Fdomiciled here but actually have
OL,13,Faccess to the British market. Now, so
OL,14,Ffar, that has proven quite effective.
